      <title>埃尔多安在土耳其市政选举中惨败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/erdogan-suffers-defeat-in-turkey-s-municipal-elections-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 在投票箱中对主要反对党遭遇了前所未有的失败，原因是通货膨胀猖獗，借贷成本达到二十多年前总统上台以来的最高水平。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/erdogan-suffers-defeat-in-turkey-s-municipal-elections-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 04:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
