    <item>
      <title>中国房屋销售持续低迷，几乎没有任何好转的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/china-home-sales-drought-persists-with-little-recovery-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月份中国房屋销售持续低迷。根据中国房地产信息集团的初步数据，继 2 月份下降 60% 后，100 家最大房地产公司的新房销售价值同比下降约 46% 至 3580 亿元人民币（496 亿美元）。资料来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-01/china-home-sales-drought-persists-with-little-recovery-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 03:36:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>外国人涌入印度债券引起市场轰动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/foreigners-flocking-to-indian-bonds-make-a-splash-across-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度被纳入主要全球债券指数的分水岭，大量资金涌入印度，正在重塑这个长期渴望免受热钱流入影响的国家的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/foreigners-flocking-to-indian-bonds-make-a-splash-across-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 01:35:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国建筑业前景黯淡，铁矿石跌至 10 个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iron-ore-sinks-to-10-month-low-on-gloom-over-china-construction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于炼钢材料面临中国建筑活动疲软和供应再度激增的双重打击，铁矿石价格跌至 10 个月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/iron-ore-sinks-to-10-month-low-on-gloom-over-china-construction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 01:27:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
